It is a great game where you can relax, play and develop a character who can do all sorts of things that you can't do in real life.  Where you can run all over the world of Norrath killing bad guys (or making a bad guy your friend..Sytox) and meeting great people from all around the world.  People who become your friends and who one day you just might meet in real life.<br>
But just like real life bad guys, really bad guys exist in EQ as well.<br>
I will share my story with you all. You have heard it before, just like I did, but I said the same thing you are thinking.  &quot;It will not happen to me, I am to careful&quot;.  <br>
On Sunday the 25th just before the 4 o'clock, I received a tell from &quot;Feigndeth&quot; (no guild attachment).  He said he was &quot;Sytox's alt and needed my help real bad, please&quot;.  &quot;Sure, old friend, what do you need, anything&quot;.<br>
You see Sytox sponsored me into the Arrows of Light when I was level 13.  I would do anything for him or anyone else in our guild.  You ask and I will do my best to help, no questions asked.<br>
He needed to borrow some pp to buy a BP for his new SK that someone was selling real cheap in the Nek Forest.  Would I loan him some pp.  &quot;Sure, I only have 4845pp in my bank, would that do?&quot;  &quot;That is fine, please bring it to the book in the Nek forest.  I will meet you there.&quot;  &quot;omw, old friend&quot;<br>
(into zone I go).. &quot;Hey old friend, here you go&quot; I hand him 4845, hit the trade button.  ....................................something starts to stink.<br>
I get a &quot;thanks&quot;, then I get a request to look at my equipment.  &quot;Can I borrow your BP, Belt and your weapon.  I really need to help this toon.  I will return it tomorrow.&quot;  Now, I am getting a little worried.  My weapon is &quot;Ranger Only&quot;.  hmmmm  &quot;Sytox, your toon is a SK it can not use my weapon.&quot;  &quot;I know&quot;, he says...  alarms are starting to go off...damn.  &quot;Hey, Feigndeth, meet me in the PoK and I will give you some armor and weapons that I have in the bank that you can use. OK?&quot;  &quot;nah, can't this computer is acting up, it crashes when I zone&quot;. ....more alarms are going off, sweaty palms I now have.  &quot;OK, give me back my pp and I will go get the armor and weapons and bring them back to you here. OK?&quot;  &quot;No, I am going to camp and Sytox will meet you in PoK&quot;.  He camps.    <br>
Damn, I have been scammed, I just know it. Damn, double damn. <br>
But I go to PoK anyway.  I wait.  I wait some more.  Oh..I am getting sick.  I contacted friends and asked if they know if Sytox had an alt named Feigndeth, but all said they not sure, but didn't think so.<br>
I wait some more, but nothing happened.<br>
Sytox someone used your name, my friend and I feel bad and sad that someone would do that.  I fell for the oldest scam around, and by posting this we can maybe stop someone else from being fooled also. <br>
I made the mistake, I acted to quickly with the hand over. It was my fault.  I petitioned and reported it, but as of this moment nothing from the GM's.  I know they can not give me back my pp, that is not the point.  I am hoping they can figure out who it was.  Probably not, he might have made the toon just to rip off people then he delete's the toon.  <br>
Anyway, you all watch out. <br>
